00:00:05.707 --> 00:00:08.241
We have had so many experiences of this,

00:00:08.321 --> 00:00:13.241
how everywhere laid down for you, everybody is looking after you.

00:00:13.321 --> 00:00:16.341
There are so many Deities who are working out things out for you.

00:00:16.421 --> 00:00:21.474
But you have to be, you have to be, extremely careful

00:00:21.554 --> 00:00:24.594
that you do not develop this fear business.

00:00:24.674 --> 00:00:27.494
Because fear takes you to the Left side

00:00:27.574 --> 00:00:32.095
and once you go to the left side, you know the
problems of the Left side is – first of all -you go against Ganesha.

00:00:32.175 --> 00:00:36.226
Ganesha is standing at the base of the Left.

00:00:36.307 --> 00:00:40.494
And then you develop cancers, you develop all these things, fear, fear, fear

00:00:40.574 --> 00:00:43.674
and emotional problems and all these things come.

00:00:44.207 --> 00:00:47.961
In emotions you should be bubbling with joy.

00:00:48.041 --> 00:00:52.641
Joy is your emotion.

00:00:52.721 --> 00:00:57.321
In action you should be thoughtless.

00:00:58.687 --> 00:01:02.554
And in ascent you should be surrendered.

00:01:03.207 --> 00:01:06.942
That’s all, it’s very simple, three mantras are very simple for children.

00:01:07.022 --> 00:01:09.208
They are like that.
